metadata.name: Meta Ape Society #1
metadata.description: From the Meta Ape kingdom, 10000 Apes will roam freely on the Ethereum BlockChain. We are a group of fun-loving anthropomorphic apes brimming with energy and optimism. We are ape chefs, ape doctors, ape engineers, ape astronauts . . . we are whoever we want to be! We live in different parts of the Metaverse, and wear distinct clothing that reflect different places, cultures, and passions. We have many stories to share, journeys to walk, and bananas to grab. Let the Meta Apes be the brand ambassadors for humanity's knowledge, creations, and everyday life.
